00:29:58.140 --> 00:30:04.590
- Ah seriously, so annoying. 
 - Look here, one, two three.

240
00:30:18.200 --> 00:30:21.040
<i>Sunbae looks alright, see? </i>

241
00:30:31.940 --> 00:30:34.220
<i>Incoming call: Jang Seo Kyeong</i>

242
00:30:37.980 --> 00:30:39.700
Yes?

243
00:30:39.700 --> 00:30:43.220
<i> I'm in front of your house. Can you come out for a moment? </i>

244
00:30:47.200 --> 00:30:49.270
What is it about?

245
00:30:49.810 --> 00:30:52.760
Jae Hyeon woke up.

246
00:30:57.780 --> 00:31:03.280
If you were worried to death like this, how did you manage to stay apart all this time?

247
00:31:08.660 --> 00:31:13.060
Did that happen while you were with Jae Hyeon?

248
00:31:16.070 --> 00:31:18.560
You can resent me.

249
00:31:20.600 --> 00:31:23.420
If I'd only gone there a bit earlier...

250
00:31:24.910 --> 00:31:27.290
I could have prevented it.

251
00:31:28.700 --> 00:31:31.860
Had I known there was someone like you,

252
00:31:32.820 --> 00:31:39.260
then I wouldn't have chased after Jae Hyeon from the start.

253
00:31:42.880 --> 00:31:44.620
I'm sorry.

254
00:31:47.940 --> 00:31:52.070
I realize that I've never properly apologized to you.

255
00:31:57.120 --> 00:31:59.400
I am really sorry.

256
00:32:00.940 --> 00:32:05.370
If you are sorry, please give up.

257
00:32:06.820 --> 00:32:09.230
I'm also tired of saying this,

258
00:32:10.570 --> 00:32:16.130
but then I won't throw hostilities and I'll stop tormenting the people around you.

259
00:32:18.160 --> 00:32:22.310
