296
00:35:26.400 --> 00:35:29.000
I can take over now, really.

297
00:35:30.400 --> 00:35:32.310
Well, that's one thing.

298
00:35:32.860 --> 00:35:37.170
On that day, you went to meet him, right?

299
00:35:38.290 --> 00:35:43.130
The day you kept looking at the clock of the hospital ward.

300
00:35:44.470 --> 00:35:45.780
Yes.

301
00:35:45.780 --> 00:35:49.780
And you two, it's true?

302
00:35:54.010 --> 00:36:00.420
