336
00:39:20.530 --> 00:39:24.510
I didn't know this.

337
00:39:24.510 --> 00:39:26.250
I am sorry.

338
00:39:26.250 --> 00:39:28.350
Do not be, Elder.

339
00:39:29.430 --> 00:39:31.960
